---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Impact" description="Real numbers from real deployments. See how direct neurofeedback is restoring lives in El Salvador and Arizona.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-white section-padding border-b border-primary/10">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="label text-primary mb-4">Impact</p>
      <div class="gold-line mb-8"></div>
      <h1 class="text-dark text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold leading-tight max-w-3xl">
        Numbers that prove what stories can't.
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- La Casa de mi Padre -->
  <section class="bg-offwhite section-padding">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_280px] gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="label text-gold mb-2">Case Study</p>
          <h2 class="mb-2">La Casa de mi Padre</h2>
          <p class="text-body/60 mb-8">El Salvador — children's home — 2+ years of deployment</p>

          <p class="text-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            La Casa de mi Padre (My Father's House) is a Christ-centered children's home caring for kids placed there by the courts after abuse, neglect, or abandonment. Children, house parents, and on-site staff all carry trauma from lives shaped by violence, poverty, and family separation. Direct neurofeedback was deployed on-site and delivered daily by a trained practitioner — the same practitioner who also serves children at our partner school, ONUVA.
          </p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gold pl-6 my-8 bg-white rounded-r-xl p-4">
            <p class="font-serif italic text-xl text-dark leading-relaxed">
              "In every student and teacher who has come through, levels of worry, anxiety, sadness, and insomnia have decreased and happiness keeps growing."
            </p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-3">— Educator at partner school ONUVA, El Salvador</p>
          </blockquote>

          <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
            The whole-community model made the difference. When everyone receives sessions — children, house parents, staff — the environment shifts. Calmer adults create calmer kids. The compound effect is measurable.
          </p>

          <!-- El Salvador Video -->
          <div class="mt-10">
            <p class="label text-gold mb-4">See the Work</p>
            <div class="aspect-video rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2jVwq9AEmBA"
                title="Restore the Last — El Salvador Documentary"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                allowfullscreen
                class="w-full h-full"
                loading="lazy"
              ></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats sidebar -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-primary">28</p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-1">participants</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-primary">97%</p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-1">showed improvement</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-primary">50%</p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-1">symptom reduction — session 1</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-primary">70%</p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-1">symptom reduction — session 7</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-primary">18,000+</p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-1">sessions delivered</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="bg-primary/10 h-px w-full"></div>

  <!-- Thrive -->
  <section class="bg-white section-padding">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_280px] gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="label text-gold mb-2">Case Study</p>
          <h2 class="mb-2">Thrive</h2>
          <p class="text-body/60 mb-8">Arizona, USA — 3+ years of use</p>

          <p class="text-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Thrive serves aged-out foster youth ages 18–25 on a 25-acre residential campus in Arizona. Most arrive over-medicated, sleep-deprived, and stuck in fight-or-flight — with years of talk therapy that never reached the root. Direct neurofeedback was added to their on-campus program three years ago.
          </p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gold pl-6 my-8 bg-light rounded-r-xl p-4">
            <p class="font-serif italic text-xl text-dark leading-relaxed">
              "It's not uncommon when we're doing neurofeedback that suddenly they just start talking — things are starting to unlock in their brain that they didn't even know."
            </p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-3">— Steve Vogel, President/CEO of Thrive</p>
          </blockquote>

          <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The results went beyond symptom relief. Residents started sleeping. Then communicating. Then earning driver's licenses and graduating high school. The nervous system calmed down — and everything else followed.
          </p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gold pl-6 my-8 bg-light rounded-r-xl p-4">
            <p class="font-serif italic text-xl text-dark leading-relaxed">
              "The results have paid for itself just exponentially."
            </p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-3">— Steve Vogel</p>
          </blockquote>

          <!-- Thrive Interview Video -->
          <div class="mt-10">
            <p class="label text-gold mb-4">Hear From Thrive</p>
            <div class="aspect-video rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ym5zkpWl2Lo"
                title="Thrive Interview — Steve Vogel"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                allowfullscreen
                class="w-full h-full"
                loading="lazy"
              ></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats sidebar -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-light rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-primary">25–30</p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-1">sessions per week</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-light rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-primary">55</p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-1">young adults housed</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-light rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-primary">10</p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-1">residents earned driver's licenses</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-light rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-primary">5</p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-1">residents graduated high school</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-light rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-primary">6,000+</p>
            <p class="text-body/60 text-sm mt-1">kids kept out of foster care</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Efficiency -->
  <section class="bg-light section-padding">
    <div class="container-narrow max-w-3xl">
      <p class="label text-primary mb-6">Why This Works</p>
      <h2 class="mb-8">Faster. Cheaper. Resolution, not management.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10">
          <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">6–12x</p>
          <p class="text-body/60 text-sm">faster resolution vs. traditional therapy</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10">
          <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">$700–$1,800</p>
          <p class="text-body/60 text-sm">total cost vs. $7,800+/year traditional</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10">
          <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">160–200</p>
          <p class="text-body/60 text-sm">clients served per practitioner/year to completion</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10">
          <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">Resolution</p>
          <p class="text-body/60 text-sm">not management — symptoms resolve, not just reduce</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-deep text-white section-padding text-center">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-white text-3xl mb-6">This isn't hypothetical. It's already happening.</h2>
      <a href="/give" class="btn-gold text-lg">Fund the next deployment</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
